      • split

        Geometry split(Geometry geometryToBeSplitted,
             Geometry splitter)
               throws GeometryOperationNotSupportedException,
                      GeometryOperationException,
                      CreateGeometryException,
                      GeometryException
        Splits the geometry by a other splitter geometry. If splitter does not intersect geometry return original geometry.
        Parameters:
        geometryToBeSplitted - to be splitted
        splitter - the geometry that splits other geometries
        Returns:
        If splitter does not intersect return original geometry, else return splitted geometry.
        Throws:
        GeometryException
        GeometryOperationNotSupportedException
        GeometryOperationException
        CreateGeometryException
